   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" xml:lang="grc" subtype="transcription" xml:id="zoor0356.transcription" corresp="#zoor0356.translation">
            <p>
               <g type="cross"/>
               <lb/>
               <choice>
                  <corr>μνημεῖον</corr>
                  <sic>Μνημῖον</sic>
               </choice> Ὄββης, ἀπο<lb break="no"/>θανούσης μετὰ καλῆς<lb/> πίστεως καὶ καλoῦ<lb/>
               ὀνόματος <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>ἐτ</abbr>
                  <ex>ῶν</ex>
               </expan>
               <num value="12">ιβʹ</num>,<lb/> ἐν μηνὶ <choice>
                  <reg>Λῴῳ</reg>
                  <orig>Λῴου</orig>
               </choice>
               <num value="4">δʹ</num>,<lb/> ἐν ἡμέρᾳ Κυρίου<lb/> τετάρτῃ. <choice>
                  <corr>Θάρσει</corr>
                  <sic>Θάρσι</sic>
               </choice>
               <corr>οὐ<lb break="no"/>δεὶς</corr>
               <sic>οὐ<lb break="no"/>δὶς</sic>
               <choice/>
               ἀθάνατος.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0356.translation" corresp="#zoor0356.transcription">
            <p> Monument of Obbe<lb/>who died having a good<lb/>name and good faith<lb/> (at the
               age) of 12 years,<lb/> on (the) 4th (day) of (the)<lb/> month Loos, on the
               fourth<lb/> day of (the) Lord (Wednesday).<lb/>Be of good cheer, no one<lb/>(is)
               immortal.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The inscription records the day of the month and the month, as well as the day of the
               week, providing the fourth day of the Lord (Wednesday), the 4th day of the month
               Loos, that is, July 23. </p>
         </div>
